 nye ordrer mens spilletiden er \"fryst\". Cossacks II: Napeolonic Wars er et godt, gammeldags strategispill som du blir skikkelig hekta p\u00e5.", "Opptur: Befriende \"gammeldags\" 2D-motor, skikkelig g\u00f8y", "Nedtur: Flytter ingen grenser, voldsomme systemkrav"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|spill"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "kultur|spill|anmeldelser"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f4eebdd4e3c81b832759e7ae5d2a77edb348067c683e371fee874098f19d6c94"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T17:44:18.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Kult-favoritt i strategisjangeren vender tilbake - bev\u00e6pnet til tennen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1138017.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/cossacksBig"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ecfa592c4eefb13669fc83e81dde729b913b8d44.jpg?5984c304"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Napoleon med sin h\u00e6r over alpene dro -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "ecfa592c4eefb13669fc83e81dde729b913b8d44"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["PC", "Game"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "PC,Game"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["anmeldelser", "spill", "kultur"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "hobbies-and-interests"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["nemlig", "stort antall", "spill", "h\u00e6r", "enheter", "alpene dro", "strategispill"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["soldiers heroes", "one", "age of empires", "cossacks ii", "ground controll", "wars", "codename panzers"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "napoleon"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/spill", "kultur", "kultur/spill/anmeldelser"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.n